summary: This is an email from an FBI dropbox system indicating that a file named 'U_Arrest_of_GHISLAINE_MAXWELL.pdf' was uploaded to UNET. The email serves as a notification of file transfer related to the arrest of Ghislaine Maxwell.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: Her name appears in the filename of the uploaded PDF, indicating the document concerns her arrest.

events.title: Upload of Ghislaine Maxwell Arrest File
events.description: A file named 'U_Arrest_of_GHISLAINE_MAXWELL.pdf' was uploaded via the FBI's dropbox system to UNET.

keyFacts: An FBI system email confirms the upload of a file concerning the arrest of Ghislaine Maxwell.
The file transfer occurred on October 4, 2021.
The document is part of internal FBI communications regarding case materials.
